node.text:
For all our fans who have seen us building this brand over the years and wanted a chance to get in on it, now is the time! Recently, changes in the rules for crowdfunding have finally made it possible for our friends, family, and fans to invest. We are excited to launch our crowdfunding campaign on @wefunder today. So if you’re trying to become partial owner of the nation’s hottest single serve wine beverage, we’re officially inviting you to the big table. All we ask is that you bring that energy we’ve seen from you all over the years!

We are so grateful for the family and friends that helped us get to this point and are excited to welcome y’all as official business partners through this campaign! If you are interested in learning more, please visit the link in our bio.

We teamed up with company co-owners, Matt and Julio from @weareGTA for the first ever World’s Tastiest Party! The party visited 8 cities and brought together more than 20,000 partiers. We had such a great time that we wanted to share the best moments with the world in this short film. @weareGTA discusses their involvement with @BeatBoxBeverages, the things that drive them to create music, and talk about each location along The World’s Tastiest Party. Enjoy!

#wearegta #beatboxbeverages #worldstastiestparty #partybetter

In Celebration of BeatBox Beverages newest flavor release, Pink Lemonade, we decided to call a few of the ladies from NewMark and host the first-ever BeatBox Boozy Brunch!  The Heart and The Hunter hosted the group at the outdoor patio of the Palihotel in West Hollywood. 
The girls indulged in sweet & savory brunch bites, followed by Pink Lemonade drinks and took to the dance floor to show YOU just how portable the World’s Tastiest Party Punch really is. 
We hope you enjoy this short video, and grab your own BeatBox at our awesome retailers across the US. You can find a store near you on the BeatBox site.
